{
  "stem": "214.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So my oldest brother and I, and some other neighbors, their sons also, and daughters-- there was a-- you know, that group of young adults-- said that we should stay there as long as we can.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Because-- so we did.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Until, when really time was getting very short, so the decision was made, you know, by the-- and also, you wondered, what is going to happen to the furniture?",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "What is going to happen-- not that we had, you know, anything so terribly valuable, but, you know, a household of so many--",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyway, so that-- that's-- that's how it happens.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember that night when we were smuggling ourselves to [?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Brejiniez ?].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were maybe 25 people sleeping on the floor there in that-- You go through this frontier in the middle of the night.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was January, I think.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was winter.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was snowing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was-- and, of course, you know, you went by horse and buggy, those things.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And so that's how I happened to come also to-- to Skierniewice.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the first couple of months, it was really considered-- I look-- I'm looking back.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was just wonderful.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We were free.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We could-- I mean, there was no ghetto.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I met-- of course, you know, my cousins were there, of my age also, younger-- a little older.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So I-- we had company, and-- and it was family, and we had an apartment which was already arranged by-- This was-- then came Passover.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And that's where this-- there was one friend of mine whom I then met-- [?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Steinschneider ?] was the family's name-- in Skierniewice also, because her family also had some relatives there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So one evening, I think in her house, I met Benno.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
